<span class="line">    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>option</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>不明<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>option</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span></span>
